WHAT IS THIS? WHAT IS NETHACK?
Nethack [https://www.nethack.org/] is a roguelike dungeon crawler released in 1987. To make a long story short, in Nethack you must obtain the fabled Amulet of Yendor and sacrifice it to your god on the Astral Plane. In this browser version*, you control your player character (pictured above as the @ symbol) by clicking adjacent tiles.
*full functionality not guaranteed
RESOURCES
I created this post using Python and the xml.etree API. You can find my Python script here [https://gist.github.com/Corncycle/6a8757009530503c934b72793752baf1#file-five-step-nethack-py]. This is not well-written code.

