osition:absolute;background:black;left:-1ch;top:0em;transform:translateZ(11px)\"\u003E.\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"position:absolute;background:black;left:-39ch;top:-17em;white-space:pre\"\u003EYou die from starvation.--More--\n                        \u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fdetails\u003E\u003C\u002Fdetails\u003E\u003C\u002Fdetails\u003E\u003C\u002Fdetails\u003E\u003C\u002Fdetails\u003E\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\n\n\u003Cdiv style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;align-items:center;width:min(100%, 59ch);font-family: sans-serif;\"\u003E\n  \u003Cdiv style=\"padding-top:10px;font-size:0.8em;text-align:center\"\u003Echrome and firefox only (ymmv on mobile)\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\n  \u003Cdiv style=\"text-align:center\"\u003Emy first original post on cohost!\u003Cbr\u003Ecan you recover the \u003Cspan style=\"color:rebeccapurple;font-weight:100\"\u003Eamulet of yendor\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E...\u003Cbr\u003E...and escape the \u003Cspan style=\"color:firebrick;font-weight:600\"\u003Emazes of menace?\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\n  \u003Cdetails style=\"width:100%\"\u003E\n    \u003Csummary style=\"font-size:0.7em;color:darkcyan;letter-spacing:0.2em;\"\u003EWHAT IS THIS? WHAT IS NETHACK?\u003C\u002Fsummary\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv style=\"padding-left:10px;padding-top:4px\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.nethack.org\u002F\"\u003ENethack\u003C\u002Fa\u003E is a roguelike dungeon crawler released in 1987. To make a long story short, in Nethack you must obtain the fabled Amulet of Yendor and sacrifice it to your god on the Astral Plane. In this browser version*, you control your player character (pictured above as the @ symbol) by clicking adjacent tiles.\u003Cdiv style=\"width:100%;text-align: right\"\u003E*\u003Cspan style=\"color:grey;font-size:0.8em\"\u003Efull functionality not guaranteed\u003C\u002Fspan\u003E\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\n  \u003C\u002Fdetails\u003E\n